items.name: Insten Silver Earphone W/mic+Film+Hard Case For Nintendo 3DS
items.shortDescription: <ul><li><b>Snap-in Crystal Case compatible with Nintendo 3DS, Clear</b></li></ul><ul><li><b>2 pc Reusable Screen Protector compatible with Nintendo 3DS</b></li></ul><ul><li><b>3.5mm In-Ear Stereo Headset, Black / Silver</b></li></ul>
items.longDescription: <b>Compatible With</b><ul><li>Nintendo 3DS</li></ul><br><b>Package Includes</b><ul><li>Snap-in Crystal Case x 1</li><li>2 pc Reusable Screen Protector x 1</li><li>Universal 3.5mm In-Ear Stereo Headset x 1</li></ul><br><b>Item Description</b><ul><li><b>Snap-in Crystal Case</b></li><li>Note: not compatible with New Nintendo 3DS</li><li>Protect your Nintendo 3DS against everyday hazards and scratches.</li><li>This crystal case is designed to offer all-around external surface protection to your Nintendo 3DS without compromising usability</li><li>Provides the maximum protection available while allowing easy access to all buttons and ports.</li><li>It molds perfectly to the 3DS's shape to highlight its beauty while providing full access to all controls.</li><li>Say goodbye to fingerprints, dust, and scratches forever</li><li>Solid see-through plastic protection</li><li>Color: Clear</li><li>Accessory ONLY. Device not included</li></ul><hr><ul><li><b>2 pc Reusable Screen Protector</b></li><li>Note: not compatible with New Nintendo 3DS</li><li>Protect your Nintendo 3DS' LCD screen against dust and scratches</li><li>Package includes 2 pieces for top and bottom LCD screen</li><li>Offers tough, durable, transparent surface while keeping the LCD screen clean and unscratched</li><li>Attaches smoothly with self-adhering surface; leaves no residue when removed</li><li>Features</li><li style="list-style: none; display: inline"><ul><li>99% UV Protection: Reduces eye strain caused by the LCD screen</li><li>Anti-Scratch Film: thickest and most durable</li><li>99% Transparent: unmatched clarity</li><li>Washable and Reusable: Never need to buy another screen protector again</li><li>Silicone Adhesive Coating: No glue residue when removed</li><li>Ultra Smooth Surface: Enhance the experience and utilization of touch screen and stylus features</li></ul></li><li>Includes</li><li style="list-style: none; display: inline"><ul><li>Reusable Screen Protector</li><li>Lint-free Cleaning Cloth</li></ul></li><li>Accessory only, Device not included</li><li>NOTE: Please do not perform installation in a dusty environment</li><li>Please read installation steps from the two tabs on the front and back protector layers before performing installation</li><li>NOTE: Please apply the screen protector gently in order to avoid too much pressure onto the screen</li></ul><hr><ul><li><b>Universal 3.5mm In-Ear Stereo Headset</b></li><li>Listen to your favorite music on the MP3 player with these high quality stereo earphones</li><li>Compact size, convenient for you to carry it in your pocket, purse or backpack</li><li>Excellent sound quality in all ranges</li><li>3.5mm headset connector is compatible with all devices with 3.5mm headset port</li><li>Color: Black / Silver</li><li>Cord Length: 42 inches</li><li>Style: In-Ear Stereo</li><li>Includes an extra pair of ear bud</li><li>Accessory ONLY, Device / MP3 player not included</li><li>Note: Apple Lightning to 3.5mm headphone jack adapter is needed to compatible with iPhone 7 /7 Plus</li></ul><ul><li>Product names are trademark of listed manufacturer or other owners, and are not trademarks of eForCity Corp.
